ent-RMCJumpsuitLiaisonOrange = orange outfit
    .desc = A pair of black pants paired with a very We-Ya orange shirt. A popular look with those in the corporate world that conduct the majority of their business from Weston Yamada offices.
ent-RMCJumpsuitLiaisonGreenWorkwear = green workwear
    .desc = A pair of brown canvas workpants paired with a green workshirt. An common pairing among blue-collar workers.
