ent-RMCJumpsuitLiaisonPilot = Weston-Yamada Pilot uniform
    .desc = A pair of grey slacks and a white button-down shirt with a dark-grey tie and golden epaulettes signifying rank; a standard uniform for a commercial grade Weston-Yamada affiliated Pilot.
ent-RMCJumpsuitLiaisonKhakiWorkwear = khaki workwear
    .desc = A pair of jeans paired with a khaki workshirt. A common pairing among blue-collar workers due to its drab look.
ent-RMCJumpsuitLiaisonPinkWorkwear = pink workwear
    .desc = A pair of jeans paired with a khaki workshirt. A common pairing among blue-collar workers due to its drab look.
ent-RMCJumpsuitLiaisonGreyWorkwear = grey workwear
    .desc = A pair of black slacks and a short-sleeve grey workshirt. Standard uniform for Weston-Yamada employees working in colony operations and administration.
ent-RMCJumpsuitLiaisonStowaway = dirty suit
    .desc = A stiff, stylish tan suit commonly worn by businessmen from the Weston-Yamada corporation. Expertly crafted to make you look like a prick.
ent-RMCJumpsuitLiaisonSkirt = liaison's skirt
    .desc = A black cardigan with a red skirt, quite fancy!
ent-RMCJumpsuitWEYATrainee = trainee's uniform
    .desc = It's a uniform with the WEYA insignia on it, with the words "Trainee" stamped below.
ent-RMCJumpsuitBlackTailored = black tailored suit
    .desc = A black suit and red tie. Very formal.
ent-RMCJumpsuitBurgundyTailored = burgundy tailored suit
    .desc = A burgundy suit and black tie. Somewhat formal.
ent-RMCJumpsuitCharcoalTailored = charcoal tailored suit
    .desc = A charcoal suit and red tie. Very professional.
ent-RMCJumpsuitNavyTailored = navy tailored suit
    .desc = A navy suit and red tie, intended for the ship's finest.
ent-RMCJumpsuitCheckeredTailored = checkered tailored suit
    .desc = That's a very nice suit you have there. Shame if something were to happen to it, eh?
ent-RMCJumpsuitJetblackExecutiveSuit = jet-black executive suit
    .desc = A formal black suit and red tie, intended for the ship's finest.
ent-RMCJumpsuitFemJetblackExecutiveSuit = fem jet-black executive suit
    .desc = A formal trouser suit for women, intended for the ship's finest.
ent-RMCJumpsuitBlackPantsUniform = simple white shirt with black pants
    .desc = It's a very simple looking white shirt and black pants.
ent-RMCJumpsuitBluePantsUniform = simple white shirt with blue pants
    .desc = A classy shirt and tie.
ent-RMCJumpsuitWornSuit = worn suit
    .desc = A washed out white shirt with a black tie and brown slacks.
ent-RMCJumpsuitGreySuitPants = grey suit pants
    .desc = A washed out white shirt with a red tie and black slacks.
